Here are prime examples of RTA laws:  <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm52.showMessage?topicID=4.topic" target="top">Rotation Entry</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> , <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm52.showMessage?topicID=5.topic" target="top">Planar Calendar Info</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> , <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm52.showMessage?topicID=8.topic" target="top">Alliances</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->.<br>
