<br>
RTA Law, the rules governing the RTA community, are -supposed to be- decided by RTA Representatives of the community.  Rotation Law, the rules governing the rotation of a mob, series of mobs, or zone on the Rathe server in the game of Everquest, are decided by those people who have completed the event being rotated.<br>
<br>
The creation and access privileges of a private forum that exists solely in this community clearly is, by definition, an RTA Law, regardless of it's content, and should be decided by the RTA Representatives, not the RTA Admins. <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->These are stupid ideas and these people should be given a damn good thrashing with a clue stick.<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.clanbashemded.org" target="top"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.clanbashemded.org/images/rigsig.gif" style="border:0;height:150;width:300;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=438887" target="top"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:white;font-family:verdana;font-size:x-small;">Magelo Profile</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#222222><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/btherathetravelagency.showUserPublicProfile?gid=baysarfk>BaysarFK</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 221<br> <font color=#00FFFF>(8/28/03 11:25 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_sunglasses.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: my 2 Plat.</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://vess.homelinux.com/funnay/spam.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/btherathetravelagency.showUserPublicProfile?gid=nazrak69>Nazrak69</A></span><br> <sp