<br>
One involves spoiling information to guilds who have no access to the Elemental Planes and, therefore, cannot possibly use the information being spoiled.  This is a BAD spoiler.  Bad Bad BAD spoiler.  Telling people how they can kill mobs they have no access to ...what kind of dumbasses do you think we are?  We aren't going to HELP you kill mobs you don't even have ACCESS to!  That's a BAD SPOILER!<br>
<br>
The second type of spoiler involves guilds who have just entered the Elemental Planes and, although they may not have yet killed any single mob IN the elemental planes, they can now have access to all the spoiler information they want AND they have the ability to USE that information to their hearts desire.  This type of spoiler is GOOD!  Good Good GOOD spoiler.  Once you get here, we'll tell you everything about the place ...you don't really have to figure it out for yourself (like we keep telling those idiots who aren't EP capable ...haha) ...come on in, be part of the family!<br>
<br>
I hope that helps clear things up for you.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>2. The forum is for the &quot;guilds&quot; involved in the rotations, yet someone not involved with said guilds has posting access?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->RTA Admins have access to all forums regardless of content for the purpose of maintenance.  This, naturally, gives them God-like abilities previously unbeknownst to the rest of the community.  No one is actually SURE of who currently has rights to that forum ...we like to keep people guessing around here.  It's easier to flame them when they don't know what the heck is going on.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>3. There are currently no rotations in the elemental planes. If there were they would be posted in the rules section correct?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->Well, you know ...funny thing about that.  Because of the unique way in which it is restricted, we in the Elemental Planes can pretty much discuss making rotations for ..well, eternity ...never actually FINALIZING any rotation while privately and secretly sharing with each other in the EP Planes forum.  Once you get there, you can have access to our sharing system ...you can't really CALL it a rotation in public (*wink* *wink*) ...because, you know, publically, we are still DISCUSSING ...but those non EP people will never know.<br>
<br>
Oh, ahem, but yeah, for the record, those rotations will be posted on the RTA board ...just as soon as they are finalized (*wink* *wink*). <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->These are stupid ideas and these people should be given a damn good thrashing with a clue stick.<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.clanbashemded.org" target="top"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.clanbashemded.org/images/rigsig.gif" style="border:0;height:150;width:300;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=438887" target="top"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:white;font-family:verdana;font-size:x-small;">Magelo Profile</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm50.showMessageRange?topicID=932.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm50.showMessageRange?topicID=932.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm50.showMessageRange?topicID=932.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm50.showMessageRange?topicID=932.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm50.showMessageRange?topicID=932.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm50.showMessageRange?topicID=932.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ftherathetravelagencyfrm50.showMessageRange?topicID=932.topic&start=121&stop=140>7</a><a href=ht